<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-1a' );" name="017-1a" class="pb">[017-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:198'>　詩總聞卷十七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='198:219'>　　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　王質　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='219:225'>　　生民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='225:232'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='232:242'>厥初生民時維姜嫄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='242:265'>　大率推本所從來多曰生民如綿民之初生此二句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='265:278'>　總起辭自此以下始列辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='278:304'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-1b' );" name="017-1b" class="pb">[017-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='304:327'>生民如何克禋克祀以弗無子履帝武敏歆攸介攸止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='327:341'>載震載夙載生載育時維后稷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='341:364'>　此總言后稷所以生也祀禖之時履帝之跡敏歆皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='364:376'>　動意也若有相感者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='376:383'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='383:407'>誕彌厥月先生如達不坼不副無菑無害以赫厥靈上帝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='407:419'>不寧不康禋祀居然生子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='419:443'>　彌月受胎盈月也先生長子也所謂無子方有子也有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='443:469'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-2a' );" name="017-2a" class="pb">[017-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='469:493'>　孕在胎則母肌膚多裂疾病多生今姜嫄無之然不安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='493:513'>　者以有感而無實居然有子懼為人所疑也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='513:520'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='520:544'>誕寘之隘巷牛羊腓字之誕寘之平林㑹伐平林誕寘之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='544:560'>寒冰鳥覆翼之鳥乃去矣后稷呱矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='560:573'>　惟其不安所以不敢育也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='573:580'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='580:602'>實覃實訏厥聲載路誕實匍匐克岐克嶷以就口食</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='602:628'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-2b' );" name="017-2b" class="pb">[017-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='628:649'>　既長大則有知識自就人求食言猶不肯育也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='649:672'>蓺之荏菽荏菽斾斾禾役穟穟麻麥幪幪𤓰瓞唪唪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='672:687'>　自能就食即能蓺種言天性也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='687:694'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='694:718'>誕后稷之穑有相之道茀厥豐草種之黄茂實方實苞實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='718:740'>種實褎實發實秀實堅實好實頴實栗即有邰家室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='740:766'>　人疑其不習而自能故知天相也今比就食初能之時又加</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='766:790'>　進也其母始即其地成其家姜嫄有邰氏之女也當是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='790:816'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-3a' );" name="017-3a" class="pb">[017-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='816:848'>　后稷婚母黨邰城在漦縣<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1073' title='KR1073' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1073.png'/>氏引此詩以為后稷之封邑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='848:855'>　　　六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='855:879'>誕降嘉種維秬維秠維穈維芑恒之秬秠是穫是畆恒之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='879:891'>穈芑是任是負以歸肇祀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='891:911'>　方任農事供國祀帝舜命播榖之時也見書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='911:918'>　　　七章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='918:942'>誕我祀如何或舂或揄或簸或蹂釋之叟叟烝之浮浮載</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='942:963'>謀載惟取蕭祭脂取羝以軷載燔載烈以興嗣嵗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='963:989'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-3b' );" name="017-3b" class="pb">[017-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='989:1015'>　自后稷未播榖之前民多阻飢祀亦不舉至此始以所登之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1015:1040'>　禾治為祀神之禮今嵗如此來嵗復然永為不易之法也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1040:1047'>　　　八章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1047:1069'>卬盛于豆于豆于登其香始升上帝居歆胡臭亶時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1069:1093'>　帝所歆歆其臭也何其臭之信得時言以時種斂故其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1093:1107'>　臭多芳也總以黍稷結郊社</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1107:1125'>后稷肇祀庶無罪悔<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>以迄于今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1125:1148'>　自后稷肇祀天下之人無罪無悔至於今皆安蓋無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1148:1174'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-4a' );" name="017-4a" class="pb">[017-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1174:1197'>　飢則自嚮善也皆由后稷肇之此詩兩稱肇祀言前</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1197:1204'>　此未有也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1204:1227'>　　聞音曰嫄魚倫切祀養里切子奬里切夙相即切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1227:1250'>　　　育越逼切達徒對切害暇憩切林自與切林叶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1250:1273'>　　　上下四句中之字各與末之字相叶但讀句至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1273:1296'>　　　中之字少止單舉隘巷平林寒冰則之字自顯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1296:1319'>　　　去起居切訏虚慮切匐蒲北切嶷魚極切幪莫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1319:1342'>　　　孔切唪布孔切道徒厚切草子苟切茂莫口切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1342:1368'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-4b' );" name="017-4b" class="pb">[017-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1368:1391'>　　　苞補掫切好許候切秠孚鄙切畆滿罪切負簿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1391:1414'>　　　猥切祀養里切揄夷周切蹂而由切叟所留切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1414:1435'>　　　軷蒲昧切烈力制切時上紙切以今單結</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1435:1458'>　　聞事曰婦人初誕子最難俗謂之頭首既先生而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1458:1481'>　　　又易亦表異也如讀作而古字多用此不必作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1481:1494'>　　　形似之如羊子之達</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1494:1517'>　　聞字曰腓肥也音肥言字之而肥也覆擁也音阜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1517:1540'>　　　言以翼而擁也腓字覆翼倒用亦下語之法此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1540:1566'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-5a' );" name="017-5a" class="pb">[017-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1566:1589'>　　　詩兩節最大一后稷初生一國祀初肇兩節皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1589:1612'>　　　作如何起辭問之其下布辭甚多問而發之則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1612:1627'>　　　從容條暢此亦下語之法</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1627:1650'>　　聞用曰肇祀郊祭也而言郊祭甚略言社祭頗詳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1650:1673'>　　　自浮浮已上郊祭也自載謀以下社祭也言載</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1673:1686'>　　　謀載惟者郊祭已畢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1686:1692'>　　行葦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1692:1699'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1699:1725'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-5b' );" name="017-5b" class="pb">[017-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1725:1748'>敦彼行葦牛羊勿踐履方苞方體維葉泥泥戚戚兄弟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1748:1762'>莫逺具爾或肆之筵或授之几</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1762:1769'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1769:1792'>肆筵設席授几有緝御或獻或酢洗爵奠斝醓醢以薦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1792:1806'>或燔或炙嘉殽脾臄或歌或咢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1806:1813'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1813:1836'>敦弓既堅四鍭既鈞舍矢既均序賓以賢敦弓既句既</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1836:1850'>挾四鍭四鍭如樹序賓以不侮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1850:1876'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-6a' );" name="017-6a" class="pb">[017-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1876:1883'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1883:1906'>曽孫維主酒醴維醹酌以大斗以祈黄耉黄耉台背以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1906:1919'>引以翼壽考維祺以介景福</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1919:1925'>　　既醉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1925:1932'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1932:1950'>既醉以酒既飽以德君子萬年介爾景福</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1950:1973'>　此人臣之辭君子斥王者也古人醇質未拘萬年之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='1973:1983'>　文然歸君上為多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='1983:2009'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-6b' );" name="017-6b" class="pb">[017-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2009:2016'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2016:2034'>既醉以酒爾殽既將君子萬年介爾昭明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2034:2041'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2041:2059'>昭明有融髙朗令終令終有俶公尸嘉告</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2059:2082'>　公而為尸者也此畢祀飲福也兩章皆言既者盡其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2082:2100'>　禮竟其事令終亦然故知是畢祀之時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2100:2107'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2107:2125'>其告維何籩豆静嘉朋友攸攝攝以威儀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2125:2151'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-7a' );" name="017-7a" class="pb">[017-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2151:2175'>　　此以下皆嘉告之辭一攝朋友先賓也二錫孝子次</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2175:2200'>　　嫡嗣也三錫祚𦙍又次庶嗣也四及臣僕又次羣臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2200:2220'>　　也五釐女士併及外孫子也又次外族也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2220:2228'>　　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2228:2248'>　威儀孔時君子有孝子孝子不匱永錫爾類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2248:2256'>　　　　六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2256:2276'>　其類維何室家之壼君子萬年永錫祚𦙍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2276:2284'>　　　　七章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2284:2310'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-7b' );" name="017-7b" class="pb">[017-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2310:2330'>　其𦙍維何天被爾禄君子萬年景命有僕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2330:2338'>　　　　八章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2338:2356'>其僕維何釐爾女士釐爾女士從以孫子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2356:2368'>　　釐臣以女者下嫁也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2368:2392'>　　　聞音曰福筆力切明謨郎切俶尺叔切告姑沃切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2392:2415'>　　　嘉居何切儀牛何切時上紙切子奬禮切壼苦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2415:2426'>　　　俊切士鉏里切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2426:2450'>　總聞曰以酒為重以食為輕人之常情又文勢如此則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2450:2476'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-8a' );" name="017-8a" class="pb">[017-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2476:2499'>語健而意長若以德為食韻既叶字亦整然古人措詞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2499:2522'>常若有更易參次葛覃薄汙我私薄澣我衣私不可以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2522:2545'>配衣采菽赤芾在股邪幅在下下不可以配股都人士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2545:2568'>帶則有餘髪則有旟餘不可以配旟鳬鷖爾酒既湑爾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2568:2591'>殽伊脯脯不足以配湑詩多如此亦非有意而然蓋承</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2591:2599'>襲習慣所致也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2599:2605'>　　鳬鷖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2605:2612'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2612:2638'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-8b' );" name="017-8b" class="pb">[017-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2638:2650'>鳬鷖在涇公尸来燕來寜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2650:2673'>　此必出都城至涇水㳺觀之間燕飲之際所見者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2673:2696'>　古禮凡飲必祭先凡祭必有尸涇水出开頭入渭安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2696:2719'>　定有臨涇及涇陽縣下章稱沙水旁曰沙稱渚水中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2719:2742'>　小洲曰渚稱潨水外之髙者曰潨稱亹山絶水曰亹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2742:2757'>　皆謂涇也大率此詩以涇為主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2757:2775'>爾酒既清爾殽既馨公尸燕飲福禄來成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2775:2782'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2782:2808'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-9a' );" name="017-9a" class="pb">[017-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2808:2831'>鳬鷖在沙公尸来燕来宜爾酒既多爾殽既嘉公尸燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2831:2838'>飲福禄来為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2838:2845'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='2845:2868'>鳬鷖在渚公尸来燕来處爾酒既湑爾殽伊脯公尸燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='2868:2875'>飲福禄来下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='2875:2882'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='2882:2905'>鳬鷖在潨公尸来燕来宗既燕于宗福禄攸降公尸燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='2905:2912'>飲福禄来崇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='2912:2938'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-9b' );" name="017-9b" class="pb">[017-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='2938:2961'>　公尸之中又其最尊者也待最尊之尸異于以次之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='2961:2976'>　尸故稍别其辭不與前後相埓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='2976:2983'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='2983:3006'>鳬鷖在亹公尸来止熏熏㫖酒欣欣燔炙芬芬公尸燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3006:3013'>飲無有後艱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3013:3036'>　所受之福禄皆今之福禄也願自是以後勿艱于錫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3036:3045'>　福言常如今也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3045:3068'>　　聞音曰沙桑何切莎與娑並以沙得音宜牛何切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3068:3095'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-10a' );" name="017-10a" class="pb">[017-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3095:3118'>　　　嘉居何切為吾禾切下後五切降乎功切亹眉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3118:3129'>　　　貧切艱居銀切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3129:3152'>　　聞跡曰亹讀如浩亹之亹水流峡㟁若門也浩亹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3152:3173'>　　　水出西塞至允吾入湟水至上邽入涇水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3173:3196'>總聞曰有尸必有祝凡此稱酒殽及福禄者皆嘏辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3196:3202'>　　假樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3202:3209'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3209:3235'>假樂君子顯顯令德宜民宜人<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>受禄于天保右命之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3235:3262'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-10b' );" name="017-10b" class="pb">[017-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3262:3268'>自天申之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3268:3291'>　唐諱皆改民為人民人衆之通稱不必分安民官人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3291:3295'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3295:3302'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3302:3328'>干禄百福子孫千億穆穆皇皇<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>宜君宜王不愆不忘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3328:3334'>率由舊章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3334:3357'>　先美後勸也君君國王王天下皆當守先世舊法也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3357:3364'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3364:3391'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-11a' );" name="017-11a" class="pb">[017-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3391:3414'>威儀抑抑德音秩秩無怨無惡率由羣匹受福無疆四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3414:3419'>方之綱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3419:3427'>　先勸後美也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3427:3434'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3434:3457'>之綱之紀燕及朋友百辟卿士媚于天子不解于位民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3457:3462'>之攸塈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3462:3485'>　全美也君燕其臣臣媚其君固足為樂君勤于君之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3485:3508'>　位臣勤於臣之位然後民安于民之所然後為樂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3508:3535'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-11b' );" name="017-11b" class="pb">[017-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3535:3558'>　　聞音曰天鐵因切命彌并切福筆力切友羽軌切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3558:3581'>　　聞訓曰今以媚為諂昔以媚為悦為愛鄭氏愛也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3581:3604'>　　　許氏説也詩兩稱媚于天子其他媚兹一人媚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3604:3620'>　　　于庶人上下皆通為美稱也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3620:3643'>　　聞句曰前兩章各三句一叶後兩章四句一叶兩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='3643:3666'>　　　句一叶吳氏以為或不用韻蓋每二句為一讀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='3666:3684'>　　　所以不叶也故談詩不可拘定律</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='3684:3706'>總聞曰此詩皆媚上之辭反覆尋之非苟為媚者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='3706:3733'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-12a' );" name="017-12a" class="pb">[017-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='3733:3739'>　　公劉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='3739:3746'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='3746:3751'>篤公劉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='3751:3774'>　公劉自邰遷豳而終能變舊漸至成邦者非厚何以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='3774:3787'>　致之此以下皆厚之迹也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='3787:3810'>匪居匪康迺埸迺疆迺積迺倉迺裹餱糧于槖于囊思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='3810:3815'>輯用光</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='3815:3839'>　行不敢居居不敢康居有積行有齎此所以相與輯而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='3839:3866'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-12b' );" name="017-12b" class="pb">[017-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='3866:3883'>　不散且有光也總言行居之大槩也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='3883:3897'>弓矢斯張干戈戚揚爰方啟行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='3897:3906'>　此整衆遷豳也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='3906:3913'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='3913:3936'>篤公劉于胥斯原既庶既繁既順迺宣而無永嘆陟則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='3936:3944'>在巘復降在原</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='3944:3967'>　此詩于京斯依于豳斯館例而推之胥恐是地名姑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='3967:3984'>　臧有揟次孟氏音子如反疑此胥也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='3984:4011'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-13a' );" name="017-13a" class="pb">[017-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4011:4025'>何以舟之維玉及瑤鞞琫容刀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4025:4048'>　雖君民雜行而上下有辨者衣服有異也此亦示衆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4048:4058'>　不慢不媟之道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4058:4065'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4065:4088'>篤公劉逝彼百泉瞻彼溥原迺陟南岡乃覯于京京師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4088:4108'>之野于時處處于時廬旅于時言言于時語語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4108:4131'>　此相都也京地名在上郡杜陽漆垣之間所謂京室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4131:4142'>　者也百泉恐即百澗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4142:4169'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-13b' );" name="017-13b" class="pb">[017-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4169:4176'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4176:4199'>篤公劉于京斯依蹌蹌濟濟俾筵俾几既登乃依乃造</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4199:4219'>其曹執豕于牢酌之用麭食之飲之君之宗之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4219:4235'>　此言定居為樂也依地名在酒泉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4235:4242'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4242:4265'>篤公劉既溥既長既景迺岡相其隂陽觀其流泉其軍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4265:4285'>三單度其隰原徹田為糧度其夕陽豳居允荒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4285:4309'>　此相地料民出軍也周制五人為伍五伍為兩計二十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4309:4336'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-14a' );" name="017-14a" class="pb">[017-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4336:4359'>　五人四兩為卒五卒為旅計五百人五旅為師五師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4359:4382'>　為軍計一萬二千五百人今計豳民以定卒伍至於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4382:4405'>　三軍而始單則合豳之境盡豳之人共得三萬七千</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4405:4428'>　五百人凡起徒役毋過家一人則是三萬七千五百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4428:4442'>　家也其餘為羡不知其幾也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4442:4449'>　　　六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4449:4472'>篤公劉于豳斯館涉渭為亂取厲取鍜止基迺理爰衆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4472:4492'>爰有夾其皇澗溯其過澗止旅迺密芮鞫之即</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4492:4519'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-14b' );" name="017-14b" class="pb">[017-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4519:4542'>　此賦工取具也皇澗過澗皆是澗名旅密芮鞫皆地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4542:4565'>　名旅以字為地名鞫以名為地名與密芮俱在隂密</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='4565:4588'>　芮城之間至今鐵器皆精唐邠州貢剪刀火筯之屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='4588:4597'>　厲鍜之餘俗也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='4597:4620'>　　聞音曰行户郎切繁汾乾切歎他涓切巘魚軒切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='4620:4643'>　　　舟之遙切京居良切野上與切依於豈切單多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='4643:4654'>　　　涓切有羽軌切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='4654:4677'>　　聞跡曰毛氏皇澗過澗皆澗名傍渭澗名甚多有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='4677:4704'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-15a' );" name="017-15a" class="pb">[017-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='4704:4727'>　　　神澗有百澗有長澗有夾澗夾澗恐是夾其皇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='4727:4750'>　　　澗酈氏渭水東而右合南山五溪水夾澗流注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='4750:4773'>　　　之恐是此澗有歴澗恐是遡其過澗合渭有長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='4773:4796'>　　　蛇水出數歴山山下有歴澗歴者過也恐是此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='4796:4822'>　　　澗又中牢水東㑹左陽水世謂之<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span>水西北出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='4822:4845'>　　　河桃谷世謂之返眼泉此地水勢逆上遡逆也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='4845:4858'>　　　恐是此澗莫得其的</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='4858:4881'>　　聞用曰舟古篆此丕形蓋在腰之象也父舟觚周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='4881:4908'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-15b' );" name="017-15b" class="pb">[017-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='4908:4917'>　　　虞敦皆然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='4917:4940'>　　聞事曰相其隂陽南北也度其夕陽東西也此以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='4940:4963'>　　　日景所測者也周制以土圭之法測土深正日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='4963:4986'>　　　景以求地中日南則景短多暑日北則景長多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='4986:5009'>　　　寒日東則景夕多風日西則景朝多隂是時已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5009:5018'>　　　有此制也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5018:5041'>總聞曰觀七月人情如此則此時雖勞民所樂從事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5041:5047'>　　泂酌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5047:5074'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-16a' );" name="017-16a" class="pb">[017-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5074:5081'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5081:5104'>泂酌彼行潦挹彼注兹可以餴饎豈弟君子民之父母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5104:5127'>　言務為省儉不為繁侈也君子如此可以為民父母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5127:5150'>　君子恐斥公劉尋詩似是草創之時逺外之地而又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5150:5163'>　在公劉之後氣象相肖也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5163:5170'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5170:5193'>泂酌彼行潦挹彼注兹可以濯罍豈弟君子民之攸歸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5193:5200'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5200:5227'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-16b' );" name="017-16b" class="pb">[017-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5227:5250'>泂酌彼行潦挹彼注兹可以濯溉豈弟君子民之攸塈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5250:5265'>　　聞音曰母滿罪切溉居氣切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5265:5288'>　　聞事曰序以為召康公戒成王凡三詩公劉則成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5288:5311'>　　　王蒞政美公劉之厚於民而獻是詩卷阿則求</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5311:5334'>　　　賢用吉士猶之可也此則言皇天親有德饗有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5334:5357'>　　　道尋詩蓋無見蓋見詩之所述者小故廣而言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5357:5380'>　　　之者大以附合其為大雅也如既醉不見太平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5380:5403'>　　　而言太平鳬鷖不見守成而言守成皆有意於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5403:5430'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-17a' );" name="017-17a" class="pb">[017-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5430:5453'>　　　附合今亦猶之可也而此則不可以不略辨或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5453:5476'>　　　者如何為德如何為道德如何親道如何饗道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5476:5499'>　　　德析為兩位親饗别為兩岐蓋自先時與後世</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='5499:5522'>　　　開拘儒曲士之門不知為序者何人其遺害未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='5522:5531'>　　　易可言也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='5531:5554'>總聞曰毛氏鄭氏泂皆逺也集韻户茗切中有逈有泂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='5554:5577'>同音各訓逈逺也泂滄也畎逈切中泂寒也胡瑩切中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='5577:5600'>有逈無泂况永切中泂亦滄也醯經涓熒欽熒三切中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='5600:5627'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-17b' );" name="017-17b" class="pb">[017-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='5627:5650'>一泂滄也一大泂地名一曰水貌一大泂地名泂一字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='5650:5673'>單起尤佳當是左氏泂酌一字不成文故加酌字盖引</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='5673:5696'>四詩皆雙名一詩難單名也細考用水貌為長水貌即</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='5696:5702'>滄也寒也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='5702:5708'>　　卷阿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='5708:5715'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='5715:5737'>有卷者阿飄風自南豈弟君子来㳺来歌以矢其音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='5737:5760'>　卷阿君子隠地也南風君子出時也卷阿之中南風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='5760:5787'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-18a' );" name="017-18a" class="pb">[017-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='5787:5810'>　之際草木茂盛風氣清美而隠居之君子来陳其所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='5810:5823'>　言也既㳺且歌喜之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='5823:5830'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='5830:5853'>伴奐爾㳺矣優㳺爾休矣豈弟君子俾爾彌爾性似先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='5853:5858'>公酋矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='5858:5865'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='5865:5888'>爾土宇昄章亦孔之厚矣豈弟君子俾爾彌爾性百神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='5888:5893'>爾主矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='5893:5920'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-18b' );" name="017-18b" class="pb">[017-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='5920:5927'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='5927:5950'>爾受命長矣茀禄爾康矣豈弟君子俾爾彌爾性純嘏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='5950:5955'>爾常矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='5955:5978'>　人君之願欲莫大于心神安且舒惟君子能使之滿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='5978:6001'>　其意繼世而長先公之遺民有功于君一也又莫大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='6001:6024'>　于土宇廣且明惟君子能使之滿其意在上而主合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='6024:6047'>　國之羣神有功于君二也又莫大于夀命之永且安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='6047:6070'>　惟君子能使之滿其意無時而不受上天之福有功</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='6070:6097'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-19a' );" name="017-19a" class="pb">[017-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='6097:6120'>　於君三也君子何負於君而不使之在位乃使之在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='6120:6133'>　野今幸其肯来不可失也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='6133:6140'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='6140:6162'>有馮有翼有孝有德以引以翼豈弟君子四方為則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='6162:6175'>　君子又可為天下之則也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='6175:6182'>　　　六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='6182:6204'>顒顒卭卭如圭如璋令聞令望豈弟君子四方為綱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='6204:6217'>　君子又可為天下之綱也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='6217:6244'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-19b' );" name="017-19b" class="pb">[017-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='6244:6251'>　　　七章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='6251:6277'>鳯凰于飛翽翽其羽亦集爰止<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>藹藹王多吉士維君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='6277:6285'>子使媚于天子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='6285:6299'>　君子又能使多士皆愛上也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='6299:6306'>　　　八章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='6306:6332'>鳳凰于飛翽翽其羽亦傅于天<span class='krp-note'>止/</span>藹藹王多吉人維君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='6332:6340'>子命媚于庶人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='6340:6354'>　君子又能使多士皆愛民也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='6354:6381'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-20a' );" name="017-20a" class="pb">[017-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='6381:6388'>　　　九章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='6388:6411'>鳳凰鳴矣于彼髙岡梧桐生矣于彼朝陽菶菶萋萋雝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='6411:6416'>雝喈喈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='6416:6439'>　鳳凰謂吉士也梧桐茂則鳳凰来君子進則多士集</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='6439:6462'>　當是卷阿之君子士望所歸民情所附能表率者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='6462:6469'>　　　十章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='6469:6492'>君子之車既庶且多君子之馬既閑且馳矢詩不多維</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='6492:6497'>以遂歌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='6497:6524'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-20b' );" name="017-20b" class="pb">[017-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='6524:6547'>　今則君子之車不患不庶且多君子之馬不患不閑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='6547:6570'>　且馳有一于此不欲多為之辭但慿歌導意而已謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='6570:6584'>　必當誠信相與久長不替也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='6584:6607'>　　聞音曰南尼心切厚狠口切主當口切卬五剛切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='6607:6630'>　　　望無方切士鉏里切使爽士切天鐵因切命彌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='6630:6645'>　　　并切喈居奚切馳居何切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='6645:6668'>總聞曰孟子所謂太公居東海之濱聞文王作興曰盍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='6668:6691'>歸乎来伯夷居北海之濱聞文王作興曰盍歸乎来此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='6691:6718'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-21a' );" name="017-21a" class="pb">[017-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='6718:6741'>来㳺来歌者雖未必二老而人品相似氣象相似要當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='6741:6764'>如二老者也尋詩他未可以當政使可當而出處進退</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='6764:6787'>之節不與㳺歌相倫太公固及見成王之朝而伯夷来</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='6787:6810'>歸之後卒以叩馬而終采薇如孟子之言後世之所取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='6810:6833'>信則此詩當歸文王或述文王之事于成王之時以相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='6833:6856'>諷勸容或有之所謂矢詩不多維以遂歌者也識者更</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='6856:6859'>詳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='6859:6865'>　　民勞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='6865:6892'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-21b' );" name="017-21b" class="pb">[017-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='6892:6899'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='6899:6917'>民亦勞止汔可小康惠此中國以綏四方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='6917:6940'>　五章皆以民亦勞止為首辭以惠此中國為次辭以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='6940:6963'>　無縱詭隨為又次辭以式遏冦虐為又次辭疲中國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='6963:6986'>　之民事外夷之域皆由詭隨者有以導上意故暴虐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='6986:6996'>　者有以害下民也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='6996:7019'>無縱詭隨以謹無良式遏冦虐憯不畏明柔逺能邇以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='7019:7024'>定我王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='7024:7051'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-22a' );" name="017-22a" class="pb">[017-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='7051:7058'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='7058:7081'>民亦勞止汔可小休惠此中國以為民逑無縱詭隨以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='7081:7102'>謹惽怓式遏冦虐無俾民憂無棄爾勞以為王休</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='7102:7125'>　當是此詩民亦勞王亦勞詭隨者亦勞故曰以定我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='7125:7148'>　王以為王休又曰無棄爾勞大率此徒本欲邀功生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='7148:7171'>　事而為固位擅權之謀其君亦欲好大喜功而為夸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='7171:7194'>　古眩今之計至於有害而無利有虧而無成則君臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='7194:7212'>　皆獘國家兩亡如晉末帝薛文遇是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='7212:7239'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-22b' );" name="017-22b" class="pb">[017-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='7239:7246'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='7246:7269'>民亦勞止汔可小息惠此京師以綏四國無縱詭隨以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='7269:7290'>謹㒺極式遏冦虐無俾作慝敬慎威儀以近有德</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='7290:7308'>　敬持已好近賢則王定王休可立致也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='7308:7315'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='7315:7338'>民亦勞止汔可小愒惠此中國俾民憂泄無縱詭隨以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='7338:7360'>謹醜厲式遏冦虐無俾正敗戎雖小子而式𢎞大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='7360:7383'>　戎雖小子言少年也而所圖甚大所謂智小而謀大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='7383:7410'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-23a' );" name="017-23a" class="pb">[017-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='7410:7427'>　力少而任重鮮不及者也責之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='7427:7434'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='7434:7457'>民亦勞止汔可小安惠此中國國無有殘無縱詭隨以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='7457:7478'>謹繾綣式遏冦虐無俾正反王欲玉女是用大諫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='7478:7501'>　王貴女之器故用女之謀至其敗事則雖欲貴女而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='7501:7524'>　不得言必至於誅戮勸之辭也我是以諫止王汝無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='7524:7543'>　以我害汝而讒我也亦防小人為後患也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='7543:7566'>　　聞音曰明謨郎切怓尼猶切國越逼切泄以世切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='7566:7593'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-23b' );" name="017-23b" class="pb">[017-23b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l413' data-llen='7593:7616'>　　　大特計切易以光大也與際叶中未大也與嵗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l414' data-llen='7616:7640'>　　　叶未見大也與未叶光大也與外叶太𤣥亦然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l415' data-llen='7640:7663'>　　　吳氏以安為於連切殘為財先切如今音自可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l416' data-llen='7663:7685'>　　　叶諫九輦切荀氏左氏皆作簡古簡讀如蹇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l417' data-llen='7685:7708'>總聞曰此小子即板之小子也是用大諫兩詩皆言之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l418' data-llen='7708:7731'>民亦勞止亦下民卒癉之意惠此中國亦曽莫惠我師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l419' data-llen='7731:7755'>之意以謹繾綣亦無為夸毗之意而式𢎞大亦憲憲泄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l420' data-llen='7755:7778'>泄謔謔蹻蹻之意無俾正敗無俾正反亦勿以為笑之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l421' data-llen='7778:7805'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-24a' );" name="017-24a" class="pb">[017-24a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l422' data-llen='7805:7828'>意大率相同甚多恐是其作同出一人所指亦為一人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l423' data-llen='7828:7843'>但此詩辭簡而肅板辭周而和也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l424' data-llen='7843:7848'>　　板</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l425' data-llen='7848:7855'>　　　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l426' data-llen='7855:7861'>上帝板板</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l427' data-llen='7861:7884'>　大率詩人之人情人事多託天為辭板板猶鬱結而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l428' data-llen='7884:7898'>　不舒人情如此可見其病也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l429' data-llen='7898:7912'>下民卒癉出話不然為猶不逺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l430' data-llen='7912:7939'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-24b' );" name="017-24b" class="pb">[017-24b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l431' data-llen='7939:7959'>　此必見民之病口為美言而身為淺謀者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l432' data-llen='7959:7977'>靡聖管管不實于亶猶之未逺是用大諫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l433' data-llen='7977:8000'>　非王如此自恣也以不誠為誠所以發女之淺謀我</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l434' data-llen='8000:8011'>　不忍坐視而諫止也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l435' data-llen='8011:8018'>　　　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l436' data-llen='8018:8041'>天之方難無然憲憲天之方蹶無然泄泄辭之輯矣民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l437' data-llen='8041:8054'>之洽矣辭之懌矣民之莫矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l438' data-llen='8054:8077'>　天乎人以為勢方危而汝情悦人以為勢方動而汝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l439' data-llen='8077:8104'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-25a' );" name="017-25a" class="pb">[017-25a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l440' data-llen='8104:8124'>　情舒汝纔發善言即可安疲民也曉之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l441' data-llen='8124:8131'>　　　三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l442' data-llen='8131:8149'>我雖異事及爾同僚我即爾謀聴我囂囂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l443' data-llen='8149:8172'>　此必所任之事不同而所聮之位則近我就女為謀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l444' data-llen='8172:8195'>　欲使女免禍而女反出多談言設辭相沮也責之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l445' data-llen='8195:8199'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l446' data-llen='8199:8217'>我言維服勿以為笑先民有言詢于芻蕘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l447' data-llen='8217:8240'>　我所言人莫不服而女獨發笑政使我不足採亦芻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l448' data-llen='8240:8267'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-25b' );" name="017-25b" class="pb">[017-25b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l449' data-llen='8267:8290'>　蕘之流先民豈肯棄也言發笑見輕也亦責之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l450' data-llen='8290:8297'>　　　四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l451' data-llen='8297:8315'>天之方虐無然謔謔老夫灌灌小子蹻蹻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l452' data-llen='8315:8338'>　天乎王方任女而虐民汝不可以為喜也我以老年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l453' data-llen='8338:8361'>　故欵以告女而汝以少年反躍以驕我也亦責之辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l454' data-llen='8361:8365'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l455' data-llen='8365:8383'>匪我言耄爾用憂謔多將熇熇不可救藥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l456' data-llen='8383:8406'>　非我年耄而言錯亂也女以憂為喜多則將熾盛雖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l457' data-llen='8406:8433'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-26a' );" name="017-26a" class="pb">[017-26a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l458' data-llen='8433:8451'>　我亦無由救藥言今尚可亦責之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l459' data-llen='8451:8458'>　　　五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l460' data-llen='8458:8476'>天之方懠無為夸毗威儀卒迷善人載尸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l461' data-llen='8476:8499'>　天乎王方任女而反怒善言女不可更以柔相順也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l462' data-llen='8499:8522'>　他日終至于迷則善人皆如尸而不復言及今未甚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l463' data-llen='8522:8537'>　善人尚肯略言也亦責之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l464' data-llen='8537:8558'>民之方殿屎則莫我敢葵喪亂蔑資曽莫惠我師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l465' data-llen='8558:8581'>　民如此受苦誰敢揆度其所以然者言不敢與此事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l466' data-llen='8581:8608'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-26b' );" name="017-26b" class="pb">[017-26b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l467' data-llen='8608:8631'>　也所以蔑資而莫肯惠衆者皆不敢與此而無與共</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l468' data-llen='8631:8642'>　謀者也亦責之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l469' data-llen='8642:8649'>　　　六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l470' data-llen='8649:8667'>天之牖民如壎如篪如璋如圭如取如㩗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l471' data-llen='8667:8690'>　天乎王之導民非難于如壎篪如圭璋取㩗則立至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l472' data-llen='8690:8712'>　言上欲定民患不舉意舉意即見效矣勸之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l473' data-llen='8712:8730'>㩗無曰益牖民孔易民之多辟無自立辟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l474' data-llen='8730:8753'>　汝不可以㩗壎篪圭璋為徒重我手也欲牖民必變</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l475' data-llen='8753:8780'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-27a' );" name="017-27a" class="pb">[017-27a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l476' data-llen='8780:8803'>　心王攜壎篪則可以誘民和攜圭璋則可以誘民莊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l477' data-llen='8803:8826'>　必至于甚變也民既多邪而女自為邪以邪濟邪此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l478' data-llen='8826:8848'>　心不易此患未艾汝何不以此告王亦勸之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l479' data-llen='8848:8855'>　　　七章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l480' data-llen='8855:8878'>价人維藩大師維垣大邦維屏大宗維翰懷德維寜宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l481' data-llen='8878:8883'>子維城</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l482' data-llen='8883:8906'>　女勿謂有藩垣屏翰懷我德而不敢動又有同宗以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l483' data-llen='8906:8929'>　為固何患乎民言雖虐民而無害不自悛也亦勸之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l484' data-llen='8929:8956'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-27b' );" name="017-27b" class="pb">[017-27b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l485' data-llen='8956:8961'>　辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l486' data-llen='8961:8971'>無俾城壞無獨斯畏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l487' data-llen='8971:8994'>　汝所恃如此不可使之壞苟壞則不獨女有所畏避</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l488' data-llen='8994:9011'>　也言同類皆蹈其患也亦勸之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l489' data-llen='9011:9018'>　　　八章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l490' data-llen='9018:9036'>敬天之怒無敢戲豫敬天之渝無敢馳驅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l491' data-llen='9036:9059'>　天乎王怒可畏女勿玩而勿恤王變可驚女勿恣而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l492' data-llen='9059:9079'>　不顧君恩不可恃少移則不保亦勸之辭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l493' data-llen='9079:9106'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-28a' );" name="017-28a" class="pb">[017-28a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l494' data-llen='9106:9124'>昊天曰明及爾出王昊天曰旦及爾㳺衍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l495' data-llen='9124:9147'>　天乎王但未明苟明則與女所出所往者盡知之王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l496' data-llen='9147:9170'>　但未旦苟旦則與爾所㳺所肆者亦盡知之也無所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l497' data-llen='9170:9193'>　憚也亦勸之辭也末章以害勸及同類蓋同惡相濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l498' data-llen='9193:9216'>　其人雖欲囘而其類未必肯囘故無獨斯畏之辭及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l499' data-llen='9216:9234'>　爾出王及爾㳺衍之辭皆善措意者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l500' data-llen='9234:9257'>　　聞音曰難泥㳂切憲虚言切輯徂合切懌弋灼切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l501' data-llen='9257:9280'>　　　囂五刀切笑思邀切屎許伊切易夷益切辟匹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l502' data-llen='9280:9307'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-28b' );" name="017-28b" class="pb">[017-28b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l503' data-llen='9307:9330'>　　　亦切翰胡干切懷胡罪切明謨郎切旦得絹切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l504' data-llen='9330:9339'>　　　衍怡戰切</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l505' data-llen='9339:9362'>　　聞事曰毛氏上帝稱王鄭氏天亦斥王也詩人措</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l506' data-llen='9362:9385'>　　　辭不如此稱帝稱天皆呼之辭而發語陳事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l507' data-llen='9385:9395'>　　　聖乃斥王也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l508' data-llen='9395:9418'>總聞曰此老而練與少而儇者之辭也終始曲折勸之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l509' data-llen='9418:9441'>無怒心無峻語至王則仍有美辭以聖言以明言以旦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l510' data-llen='9441:9453'>言斯人其愛君憂國者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l511' data-llen='9453:9480'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0014', 'WYG', '017-29a' );" name="017-29a" class="pb">[017-29a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
